metadata.name: Invisible City #1
metadata.description: Generative geometry by Frederik Vanhoutte, @wblut | 10000 x 10000 PNG | February 2023 | One of 512 single image fictions of struggle and harmony, growth and decay, disease and healing, order and disorder | Structures and compositions inspired by cellular, organic, mineral, anthropogenic, geological complexity | Color palettes inspired by Albertus Seba, Ernst Haeckel & Adolf Giltsch, and Gottlob Werner & Patrick Syme
